data.eml:eml: Four species of Tubifex Lamarck (Annelida: Oligochaeta: Naididae) from Tibet, China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cui, Yongde (2017): Four species of Tubifex Lamarck (Annelida: Oligochaeta: Naididae) from Tibet, China. Zootaxa 4320 (2): 366-378, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4320.2.10
